PrecisEnactment of the RADIOCOMMUNICATION ACT (SUBSECTION 4(1) AND PARAGRAPH 9(1)(b)) EXEMPTION ORDER (SECURITY AND SAFETY, INTERNATIONAL RELATIONS AND NATIONAL DEFENCE), NO. 2002-2 - which exempts the RCMP and the Canadian Forces from the application of the Act with respect to interfering with radiocommunication signals during The Pope's visit to Toronto in July 2002.
